HEADWORD: Chockablock
<hw>Chock"a*block</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<def>Hoisted as high as the tackle will admit; brought close together,
as the two blocks of a tackle in hoisting.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

